channel.description:
Okay guys!
This is how you can change the armour that a new player starts with.
Difficulty 0.5/10 [b]REALLY[/b] easy ;).
Files edited:[b]player.java[/b]
Okay let's get started!
                            [b]open up player.java[/b]
Search for:
[code]playerEquipment[playerHat][/code]
and you should see this:
[code]		playerEquipment[playerHat]=2910;
		playerEquipment[playerCape]=4405;
		playerEquipment[playerAmulet]=6585;
		playerEquipment[playerChest]=2906;
		playerEquipment[playerShield]=3842;
		playerEquipment[playerLegs]=2495;
		playerEquipment[playerHands]=2912;
		playerEquipment[playerFeet]=2904;
		playerEquipment[playerRing]=6737;
		playerEquipment[playerArrows]=882;
		playerEquipment[playerWeapon]=4587;[/code]
all the..
[code]playerWeapon playerArrows[/code]
.. and stuff means that fx. if your
[code]playerEquipment[playerWeapon]=4587;[/code]
that means the new players that logs in is wearing dragon scimitar (4587 = item ID for dragon scimitar ;)).
So change it to whatever you want ;).
                              [b][size=14pt]Done ;)! That's all for now hope you enjoyed! Any questions or errors? Post in reply! ;).[/size][/b]
